            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had the privilege of enrolling my child at CJM Waverley School in Mussoorie, and I can confidently say that it has been one of the most rewarding decisions we've made for our child's education. From the picturesque location to the dedicated faculty and vibrant learning environment, CJM Waverley School has exceeded our expectations in every way.\n\nThe school is committed to providing a holistic education that encompasses not only academic excellence but also character development.\n\nThey offer a plethora of extracurricular activities ranging from sports to arts and culture. These activities not only nurture talents but also instill discipline, teamwork, and leadership skills in the students.\n\nIn conclusion, CJM Waverley School in Mussoorie is a gem in the world of education. It goes beyond academics to nurture well-rounded individuals who are not only knowledgeable but also compassionate and socially responsible. If you're looking for a school that values education, character, and holistic development, CJM Waverley School is the perfect choice.",
